sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Server as Regex Detector<br/>Axum Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Detectors as Detection Engine<br/>(Built-in + Custom)

    Note over Orchestrator,Detectors: Flow 1: Health Check
    Orchestrator->>Server: GET /health<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>No Auth
    Server-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK "healthy"

    Note over Orchestrator,Detectors: Flow 2: Text Content Detection (Built-in PII)
    Orchestrator->>Server: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>No Auth<br/>Content-Type: application/json
    Note right of Server: Request body includes<br/>text content + detector names<br/>(email, ssn, credit_card)
    Server->>Detectors: Lookup named detectors<br/>in HashMap
    Detectors->>Detectors: Compile & execute<br/>built-in regex patterns
    Detectors-->>Server: Match results with<br/>start/end offsets
    Server-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK<br/>[[{start, end, text,<br/>detection: "pii",<br/>detection_type: "email",<br/>score: 1.0}]]

    Note over Orchestrator,Detectors: Flow 3: Text Content Detection (Custom Regex)
    Orchestrator->>Server: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>No Auth<br/>Custom regex pattern in body
    Server->>Detectors: Compile custom regex<br/>per-request (no caching)
    Detectors->>Detectors: Execute regex<br/>against text content
    Detectors-->>Server: Match results with<br/>start/end offsets
    Server-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK<br/>[[{start, end, text,<br/>detection: "custom",<br/>detection_type: "regex",<br/>score: 1.0}]]
